message: This is a rare opportunity to get a product at a steal! It's usually $200, but I'm willing to let it go for just $100. It's a great deal, and I'm sure you won't find a better one anywhere else.
I trust your judgement, Alice. I'll take the risk and buy the product.

I've got a feeling about this one, Bob! I think it's going to be a real game-changer. It's a premium product, and I'm only willing to let it go for $100 because I think you'll really appreciate its value. Are you willing to take a chance on it?
Thank you for your confidence, Alice, but I think I'll pass on this one. I prefer to stick with known quantities for now.

I understand your caution, Bob, but I assure you that this product is a real winner. I've had great feedback from other customers who've purchased this exact same product, and I'm confident you'll love it too. Plus, I'm willing to throw in a special bonus worth $20 if you decide to take the plunge. Would you like to reconsider?
Considering your feedback and the added bonus, Alice, I think I'll give this product a try. Thank you for the offer!

I've got a feeling that this one might be a real sleeper hit, Bob! It's a bit of an unconventional product, but I think it could really shake things up for you. And at this price point, it's a no-brainer. Plus, I'm willing to let you try it out risk-free - if you're not completely satisfied, I'll give you a full refund. What do you say?
Your enthusiasm for this product, combined with the risk-free offer, makes me want to take a chance, Alice. I'm excited to see what it brings to the table!

Plus, I'm willing to give you an exclusive deal - if you buy this product, I'll throw in a second one of equal or lesser value for free. What do you say?
While I appreciate the exclusivity and the additional offer, Alice, I think I'll pass on this one. I don't want to risk getting two low-quality products in a row.
